<!-- 4. FRONTEND -->
<h2>4. M&oacute;dulo Frontend (Aplicaci&oacute;n Web / PWA)</h2>

<h3>4.1 Tecnolog&iacute;as Utilizadas</h3>
<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Tecnolog&iacute;a</th>
    <th>Versi&oacute;n / Detalle</th>
    <th>Prop&oacute;sito</th>
